I moved the check from RPC to the wallet.

On a related note, I have in a [work in progress branch](https://github.com/Sjors/bitcoin/tree/2019/06/TransactionError) which replaces all `_failReason`  occurrences with `TransactionError`.

@promag I'd rather not change the GUI messaging here.

